OL,3,CTwo further arrests after three-month-
OL,4,Cold girl dies in dog attack
OL,6,FA further two people have been
OL,7,Farrested following the death of a
OL,8,Fthree-month-old girl in a dog attack
OL,9,Fon Teesside.
OL,11,FPolice were called to a property on
OL,12,FHardale Grove, in the Dormanstown area
OL,13,Fof Redcar, shortly after 1.30pm on
OL,14,FThursday afternoon (9 April).
OL,16,FArmed officers destroyed a dog on the
OL,17,Fstreet, meanwhile another dog
OL,18,Frecovered at the property was
OL,19,Fdestroyed later.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
