PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776276671
OL,3,CTwo further arrests after three-month-
OL,4,Cold girl dies in dog attack
OL,6,FMeanwhile, in an update released on
OL,7,FMonday (13 April), officers confirmed
OL,8,Fthat a 31-year-old woman has been
OL,9,Farrested on suspicion of child neglect
OL,10,Fand being a person in charge of a dog
OL,11,Fdangerously out of control resulting
OL,12,Fin death. A 36-year-old man has also
OL,13,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of being a
OL,14,Fperson in charge of a dog dangerously
OL,15,Fout of control resulting in death.
OL,16,FThey have both been released on
OL,17,Fconditional bail.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
