PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776276671
OL,3,CTwo further arrests after three-month-
OL,4,Cold girl dies in dog attack
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Rachel Stockdale,
OL,7,FHead of Local Policing at Cleveland
OL,8,FPolice, said: "Our thoughts continue
OL,9,Fto be with the child's family
OL,10,Ffollowing this tragic and distressing
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,F"I want to take this opportunity to
OL,14,Frequest that their privacy is
OL,15,Frespected during this difficult time.
OL,17,F"There will continue to be a scene in
OL,18,Fplace at the property alongside a
OL,19,Fvisible policing presence as the
OL,20,Finvestigation is ongoing.
